summary: This mod revamped eight female npcs in skyrim.
descriptionHtml:
[color=#b6b6b6][font=Trebuchet MS][size=2]
Replaced eight female npcs in skyrim.
Including:
Iona
Lydia
Jordis the Sword-Maiden
Jenassa
Mjoll the Lioness
Legate Rikke
Serana
Elisif the Fair
All characters were made by four different persons from the Dragonsreach mod team.
